tting precedent for future interactions with my clients I am mindful I am shaping my own work environment by my actions today I am striving to balance my desire for efficiency with my need for clarity and accountability I am recognizing I am responsible for my own actions and their long-term impact on my professional reputation I am committed to finding solution where all my stakeholders are considered I am open to alternative solutions I am ready to listen to my client I am prepared to explain my reasoning I am focused on my own growth and my own learning I am eager to understand my own biases I am curious about my own motivations I am interested my own values I am attentive to my own emotions I am present with my own thoughts I am honest with myself I am kind to myself I patient with myself

